%section
  %h2 Additional Details
  %ul
    %li
      %strong Covid-19:
      The data points for April 2020 through July 2022 reflect closures at the libraries due to COVID-19. 
    %li
      %strong Table Construction:
      The Card Swipe table has two columns of user type information. 
      The “user_group” column is extracted from Alma demographics.
      It distinguishes between staff that are taking classes (who may be listed as “student” in usc_desc) and full time students.
      The Alma demographic tables are snapshots of a person's affiliation at a point in time. 
      These tables were not added until 2022, hence, user types and affiliations before that are unreliable.
      There will be descrepancies between the demographics tables and the Institutional Research counts.
    %li
      %strong Deduplication:
      Additional processes occur to reduce the number of duplicate swipes at an entrance. 
    %li
      %strong Demographic Enrichment:
      The Biotech Library data was manually recorded from 2016-2020.
      When it was renovated into the Holman Biotech Commons, Public Safety installed card swipe machines.
      The legacy data is available in the Legacy Biotech Counts table. 
